trans-unit.source: Defines a circular hot spot region in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en sirkulær hot sted område i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: This class defines a circle-shaped hot spot region in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen definerer en sirkel-formet hot sted område i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: To define the region of the CircleHotSpot object, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.X%2A> property to the value that represents the x-coordinate of the center of the circular region.
trans-unit.target: For å angi område for CircleHotSpot-objektet er angitt i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.X%2A>egenskapen verdien som representerer x-koordinaten for senterpunktet i sirkulære området i.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.X%2A>

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Y%2A> property to the value that represents the y-coordinate of the center of the circular region.
trans-unit.target: Angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Y%2A>egenskapen verdien som representerer y-koordinaten for senterpunktet i sirkulære området i.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Y%2A>

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Radius%2A> property to the distance from the center of the circle to the edge.
trans-unit.target: Angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Radius%2A>egenskapen avstanden fra midten av sirkelen kanten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Radius%2A>

trans-unit.source: When a CircleHotSpot control is clicked, the page either navigates to a URL, generates a post back to the server, or does nothing.
trans-unit.target: Når en CircleHotSpot kontroll, siden enten navigerer til en URL-adresse, genererer en post på serveren eller gjøre noe.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> property specifies this behavior.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>egenskapen angir dette problemet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: To navigate to a URL, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> property to `HotSpotMode.Navigate`, and use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A> property to specify the URL to navigate to.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil navigere til en URL-adresse, kan du angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>egenskapen `HotSpotMode.Navigate`, og bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A>til å angi URL-adressen til å navigere til.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: To post back to the server, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> property to `HotSpotMode.PostBack`, and use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A> property to specify a name for the CircleHotSpot object.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil legge til serveren, kan du angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>egenskapen `HotSpotMode.PostBack`, og bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A>til å angi et navn for CircleHotSpot-objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: This name will be passed in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs> event data when the CircleHotSpot is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Dette navnet vil bli sendt i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs>Hendelsesdata når CircleHotSpot klikkes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: If you want the CircleHotSpot object to have no behavior, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> property to `HotSpotMode.Inactive`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil CircleHotSpot-objektet har ingen virkemåte, angitt i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>egenskapen `HotSpotMode.Inactive`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot> class.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å initialisere en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: Returns a string that represents the x- and y-coordinates of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"></xref> object's center and the length of its radius.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en streng som representerer x - og y-koordinatene til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"> </xref> objektets center og lengden på radien.

trans-unit.source: This method uses the values assigned to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.X%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Y%2A> properties to return the center coordinates and the value assigned to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Radius%2A> property to return the radius.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden brukes verdiene som er tilordnet til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.X%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Y%2A>Egenskaper for å returnere center koordinatene og verdien som er tilordnet til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Radius%2A>til å returnere radiusen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Radius%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Y%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.X%2A>

trans-unit.source: The GetCoordinates method is used internally by ASP.NET to get the text to use for the coordinates of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot> when it is rendered.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetCoordinates brukes internt ASP.NET teksten skal brukes for koordinatene til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>når den gjengis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: A string that represents the x- and y-coordinates of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"></xref> object's center and the length of its radius.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer x - og y-koordinatene til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"> </xref> objektets center og lengden på radien.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the distance from the center to the edge of the circular region defined by this <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir avstanden fra center kanten av sirkulære området som er definert av dette <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The Radius property allows you to get or set a value that represents the distance in pixels from the center to the edge of the circular region defined by this <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot> object.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Radius gjør det mulig å hente eller angi en verdi som representerer avstanden i piksler fra center kanten av sirkulære området som er definert av dette <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: To completely define a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot> object, you must specify a value for the Radius property as well as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.X%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Y%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Fullstendig definere en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>objektet, må du angi en verdi for egenskapen Radius i tillegg til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.X%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Y%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Y%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.X%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: An integer that represents the distance in pixels from the center to the edge of the circular region defined by this <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som angir hvor mye i piksler fra center kanten av sirkulære området som er definert av dette <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The default is 0.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 0.

trans-unit.source: The specified value is less than 0.
trans-unit.target: Den angitte verdien er mindre enn 0.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the x-coordinate of the center of the circular region defined by this <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir x-koordinaten for senterpunktet i sirkulære området som er definert av dette i <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The X property allows you to get or set a value that represents the x-coordinate of the center of the circular region defined by this <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot> object.
trans-unit.target: X-egenskapen kan du hente eller angi en verdi som representerer x-koordinaten for senterpunktet i sirkulære området som er definert av dette i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: To completely define a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot> object, you must specify a value for the X property as well as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Y%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Radius%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Fullstendig definere en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>objektet, må du angi en verdi for egenskapen X i tillegg til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Y%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Radius%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Radius%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Y%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: The x-coordinate of the center of the circular region defined by this <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: X-koordinaten for senterpunktet i sirkulære området som er definert av dette i <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The default is 0.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 0.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the y-coordinate of the center of the circular region defined by this <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir y-koordinaten for senterpunktet i sirkulære området som er definert av dette i <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The Y property allows you to get or set a value that represents the y-coordinate of the center of the circular region defined by this <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot> object.
trans-unit.target: Y-egenskapen kan du hente eller angi en verdi som representerer y-koordinaten for senterpunktet i sirkulære området som er definert av dette i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: To completely define a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot> object, you must specify a value for the Y property as well as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.X%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Radius%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Fullstendig definere en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>objektet, må du angi en verdi for egenskapen Y i tillegg til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.X%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Radius%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.Radius%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot.X%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: The y-coordinate of the center of the circular region defined by this <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot"></xref> object.
